      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEETKINDOFMAGIC (4) finished eighth last start over 1800m at this track, beaten 24 metres, after filling a minor placing at the previous appearance over 1800m at this track. This should be an easier assignment so he is sure to prove tough to beat. PARADIGM (3) raced in a handy position last start and finished fourth, beaten 6 metres, in a far better performance at this track over 1800m. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Finds a nice race and will take plenty of beating once more. HY FILANTE (5) has been thereabouts of late and is a great chance to break through. Good effort last time out when he finished fourth at this track over 1800m. DASHING COWBOY (7) got the prize two runs back. Then, things went sour last time when he broke and finished 19 metres back in seventh over 1800m at this track. A wide gate is no help, but he is still worth including in all top 4 combos to be safe.",
